title: Do Photos Show Boys in ‘Team Mitch’ Shirts Choking and Kissing AOC Cutout?
subtitle: The photos were taken at “Kentucky's biggest political picnic.”
author: Alex Kasprak
vclaim: A photograph shows several young males wearing “Team Mitch” shirts while strangling, kissing, or otherwise posing with a cardboard cutout of U.S. Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez.
